  "detailed_description": "<strong>Your driving and choices will change your destiny⸺</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/8dc99358586391be380053cba9bc614f.poster.avif?t=1593299971\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/8dc99358586391be380053cba9bc614f.webm?t=1593299971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/8dc99358586391be380053cba9bc614f.mp4?t=1593299971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>『Tales in the TAXI』 is a multi-ending adventure game in which the story diverges by driving a taxi and talking with passengers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Driving Part : Take our passengers where they want to go!</h2>A wide variety of  passengers are rode in the taxi!<br>Let's understand their intentions and take them to the proper destination!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/0fc0a000ff34f953660cbe867a1ba5e4.poster.avif?t=1593299971\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/0fc0a000ff34f953660cbe867a1ba5e4.webm?t=1593299971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/0fc0a000ff34f953660cbe867a1ba5e4.mp4?t=1593299971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conversation Part : Listen to passengers' problems and select appropriate solutions!</h2>The passengers in this taxi are having some kind of problem.<br>Let's listen carefully to their worries and choose the best answer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/2b4f78d7e1c0ea093da20925e7de03ed.poster.avif?t=1593299971\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/2b4f78d7e1c0ea093da20925e7de03ed.webm?t=1593299971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249390/extras/2b4f78d7e1c0ea093da20925e7de03ed.mp4?t=1593299971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
